SpookyHash version 2 for ATS2/Postiats
--------------------------------------

No garbage collector is required, and exceptions are not used.

There is also a C interface that has no other dependencies and
requires no garbage collector.

FIXME: Platforms requiring alignment to 64-bit boundaries should work,
as should big-endian platforms, but the package has not yet been
tested on such platforms.

FIXME FIXME FIXME: TEST ON SUCH PLATFORMS AND FIX ANY BUGS THAT ARE
                   REVEALED.

Mac OS/X universal binaries currently are not supported.

